  "title": "Sales Executive- Construction Industry",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview</strong></p><p>We specialise in customised illuminated signages for shops and buildings- MNCs, NGOS, Government sector, SMEs and more.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Apex Signages seeks a dedicated Sales Executive to drive business growth by managing sales inquiries, processing orders, negotiating with customers, and building lasting client relationships.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Respond promptly to inbound sales inquiries to provide accurate product information and support customer decision-making</li><li>Process sales orders efficiently to ensure timely and accurate fulfillment</li><li>Conduct customer negotiations professionally to secure favorable sales agreements</li><li>Build and maintain long-term relationships with customers to encourage repeat business and loyalty</li><li>Achieve and exceed sales targets through proactive sales efforts and effective customer engagement</li><li>Generate new business opportunities by identifying and pursuing prospects among existing and potential customers</li><li>Collaborate with internal teams and external partners to coordinate sales activities and deliver customer solutions</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Fluent in English and Mandarin, both spoken and written, to communicate effectively with diverse customers</li><li>Proven experience in a sales role demonstrating ability to meet sales goals</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office Suite (Word, Excel, Outlook) to manage sales documentation and communication</li><li>Strong attention to detail to ensure accuracy in sales orders and customer information</li><li>Ability to work independently and collaboratively within a team environment</li><li>Positive attitude and strong work ethic to contribute to a supportive workplace culture</li></ul><p>Benefits</p><ul><li>Competitive salary of $3000, plus monthly bonuses based on sales performance</li><li>Opportunities for professional growth and development</li><li>A supportive and collaborative work environment</li><li>Inclusive workplace valuing diversity and encouraging candidates of all backgrounds to apply</li></ul>",
